  "title": "AB03 - Afterschool Care Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position title : Afterschool Care Teacher</strong></p><ul><li>Location: Woodleigh </li><li>Working Days: 5.5day</li><li>Working Hours -Monday to Friday 1030am to 7pm- Saturday 9.30am to 1.30pm</li><li>Salary : $2,200 - $3,400</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Implement the program for the class in accordance with the policies, guidelines, framework and philosophy of the centre.</li><li>Guide primary school children (primary 1 to 5) to ensure completion of daily homework.</li><li>Keep accurate records of children’s progress and address each child’s educational and developmental needs on an individual basis to the best of your ability.</li><li>Responsible for the preparation and upkeep of teaching resources, arrangement, appearance and learning environment of the classroom.</li><li>Maintain and build relationships with children and parents.</li><li>Conduct unique enrichment programmes.</li><li>Ensure safety and timely transfer of students from school to student centre.</li><li>Ensure safety of children within the premises.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as delegated by Centre Director.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or higher in any discipline with minimum of 2 years of teaching experience with primary school students.</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
